*oooook kiddies. its been a long time since ive updated again. so heres whatz been happening. last entry it said how john and i were getting engaged in december...well...september 23, he suprised me and asked me then!!! it wuz so cute! i wuz in the shower, then i came out in2 the living room after, and all these candles were lit, and he wuz there waiting on one knee! it wuz awesome. december 16 - 20 the 2 of us are going 2 orlando. we're staying @ this really gorgeous resort right by universal. its going 2 be really awesome. i cant wait! so many shitty things have happened tho. 2 weeks ago i got really sick, then the week after johns grandfather died, then this week im sick (not as bad) and my dads aunt is in the hospital.
*last nite johns younger brother nick (a.k.a broseph ---only i can call him that:-D---) had a party since johns parents are gone till tuesday. and there wuz like 15-20 high school kids running around getting fucked up. me, john, derek and jess all just hung out, drank and played some hold'em. it wuz an interesting evening 2 say the least.
*2morros the steeler game!!!!!! im sooooo xcited! we're leaving @ like...7 am, and tailgating and getting drunk till the game starts @ 1. we're in the club seats so its gonna kick so much ass. im sooooo bummed about big ben tho:( that makes me sad. but ill wear my jersey and show my support for president roethlisberger!!! but anywayz, im out

ok well...wow. been awhile. but anywayz...the greatest news ever...john and i are getting engaged in december!!!! he bought the ring yesterday. (its gorgeous BTW) and i couldnt be happier. but anywayz...im not really sure what 2 talk about. the YSU penguins are kicking ass. we're 3-0. we won yesterday 42-0!! its crazy! next week we're playing @ heinz field. im xcited. but anywayz, im out

wow, its been SOOO long since ive updated this thing! but the internet has been down @ school becuz of the strike, so i can only get on when im @ home. but anywayz, last nite wuz the frist YSU football game...we played slippery rock...which is johns school, and KiLLED them. 44-14. it wuz awesome...that meant john had 2 drink an entire bottle of captain morgan. it wuz funny as shit. mondays my birthday :-D yay me. its gonna be a fun weekend. but anywayz, im out

this all seems so surreal 2 me right now...2day is by far the worst day of my life. i got a call last nite from my mom saying that my grandpas in the hospital again. they think he had a mild stroke...then 2day, my mom called and told me 2 more things 2 add on 2 that. my cousin mike (a close cousin) was killed in a car accident this morning (thatz another cousin lost 2 a drunk driver) and then i find out the icing on the cake. the doctors office called 2 remind us of my appointment 2morro, and 2 tell my mom what papers she needed 2 bring and all that jazz, and they mentioned me getting more xrays on my back. my mom wuz like "well that's 2 see how her scoliosis is doing right?" and they said..."well no actually...last time she wuz here, we found something in her back that we think might be precancerous...so we need 2 check that out." ok...now its time for me 2 flip out. WTF?! y the hell wouldnt u tell me that when u fucking found it? i mean jesus christ, this isnt xactly the best news ive heard...now this is happening 2 me...AGAiN. wow...what a great fucking day...

wtf...its 7:43...and im awake. i couldnt fall asleep 2 save my life last nite, so theres no point in trying now. i pierced my lip 2day. it looks awesome. its on the left side. i couldnt put it in the middle cuz i wouldnt be able 2 play the clarinet. but anywayz, nothin 2 write about...im out

i fucking hate insomnia! thatz a WEEK now i havent been able 2 fall asleep. its really started 2 piss me off. yesterday when i got back 2 the apartment shanthony and i ordered pizza and watched house of 1000 corpses, then shanthony jeff and i went 2 go see meet the fockers @ the cheap seats. (even tho jeff and i both had already seen it) then when we got back we watched paycheck, and cooked chicken, then watched some family guy on dvd, and when shannon fell asleep anthony and i played xbox, then i came back in2 my room when they went 2 bed, and dyed my hair. :) yay. i have black hair now. but anywayz, im out

i am totally amazed right now. its a saturday...and i just woke up @ 4:00 pm. but the amazing thing is, my mom didnt come in and go apeshit like she usually does when i sleep 1 minute over 12:00. its probably becuz ive had insomnia for the past 5 nites...and it takes about 6 hours till i can fall asleep. anywayz, last nite i came up, then went 2 see the amityville horror w/scott, then we made our traditional taco bell run, then i came back, ate my taco bell, and watched spiderman 2. (i had a craving 2 watch it) then i went upstairs and attempted 2 fall asleep. then it started 2 thunderstorm, and i wuz listening 2 it, and watching the lightning light up my room. then finally i fell asleep. 2day we're going 2 go 2 the mall, then probably go see a movie. but anywayz, im out

well...its now 4.20. its been a year since jess and darren died. i can still remember what happened. i woke up 2 a phone call @ 3:45 am saying that they were on their way back from a meeting in florida @ the church they were going 2 get married @...and they were hit by a drunk driver. darren died instantly, but jess got pinned 2 the dashboard and burnt 2 death. she wuz my best friend. i miss u guys both so much, and ill never forget u.

*life aint alwayz what it seem 2 be
words cant xpress what u mean 2 me
even tho ur gone, we're still a team
thru ur family, ill fulfill ur dreams
in the future i cant wait 2 see
if u open up the gates for me
reminisce, sometime

try 2 black it out
but it plays again

after death

every single day, every time i pray
ill be missin u
thinkin of that day, when u went away

ill be missin u
its kinda hard w/u not around

watchin us while we pray for u
everyday we pray for u
til the day we meet again
in my heart is where ill keep u friend
memories give me the strength i need 2 proceed
strength i need 2 believe*

anywayz...2day i have 2 go home for counseling @ 5...then who knos whatz goin on after i get back up here. last nite i ended up scratchin the hell outta my wrists. i didnt mean 2 tho. i wuz thinking, and i just looked down afterwards and there the scratches were. but anywayz...i should try and get some sleep.

--its so hard 2 hide how i feel inside
when everyday i live a lie
a painted smile thatz begun 2 fade
i cant fix the mistakes ive made
im breaking down, and soon ull see
all the shattered dreams inside of me
my finger rests on the trigger of my loneliness
waiting for the right time 2 end all this
no matter what people say, id rather bleed the thoughts away
until im just an empty shell
and ill feel the feeling i kno 2 well
as i drift deeper in2 my own little hell
where the only escape is a razor blade
as i watch while all these memories fade
my scars remind me of how it feels
when theres nothing left, and i cant deal
w/everything that brings me down
staring @ the ceiling as im lying on the floor
i cant take this life anymore
im stained w/crimson regret that wont ever go away
and as the darkness overcomes
and once again im empty and numb
i realize that the only thing that i can do
is let go, and surrender--
*by me...april 19, 2005*

well last nite sux. i didnt get ANY sleep. i laid in bed all nite, and couldnt fall asleep. so...that sucked. i finally fell asleep @ 10. i just woke up. so that sucked. had a rough nite tho so...but anywayz, scott came out last nite, and me, him, shanthony, jeff, and ricky went bowling. jeff and ricky left early, but we had a good time. then after bowling i came back, had some lasagna, watched family guy, then ATTEMPTED 2 go 2 bed. but im out like a fat grrl in dodgeball

what a day. i woke up, went tanning...came back, washed my car, worked in the yard all day...worked on my car, went 2 blockbuster got ladder 49, then came back, played some ps2, then watched it. it wuz really good. o yea, i made some really good steak 2day 2. mmm, it wuz good. but anywayz, 2days my dads birthday, so after dinner i gotta go back 2 my apartment. but im out

just when i think uve got everything figured out, life throws u a curve ball, and ur right back 2 where u started. which for me is nowhere. i guess i should be used 2 this by now, but...needless 2 say, im not. o well...i guess i mite as well get used 2 it. nothings ever gonna change...im out
